{#-jinja2: trim_blocks: True, lstrip_blocks: True #}
## INFORMATION FROM THE GITHUB ISSUE:

**Issue title:**  
{{ structured_issue_data.issue.title }}

**Labels:**  
{%- if structured_issue_data.issue.labels %}
{%- for label in structured_issue_data.issue.labels %}
{{ label.name or "N/A" }}  
{%- endfor %}
{%- else %}
_No labels provided._  
{%- endif %}

**Issue body:**  
{%- if structured_issue_data.issue.body %}
{{ structured_issue_data.issue.body.strip() }}  
{%- else %}
_No issue body provided._  
{%- endif %}

**Comments:**  
{%- if structured_issue_data.issue.comments %}
{%- for comment in structured_issue_data.issue.comments %}
{%- set body_lines = comment.body.strip().splitlines() %}
- Author commented on **{{ comment.created_at }}**:  
{%- for line in body_lines %}
    {{ line }}  
{%- endfor %}
{%- endfor %}
{%- else %}
_No comments provided._  
{%- endif %}

**Image links:**  
{%- if structured_issue_data.images %}
{%- for image_url in structured_issue_data.images %}
- {{ image_url }}  
{%- endfor %}
{%- else %}
_No images provided._  
{%- endif %}

**Linked PRs:**  
{%- if structured_issue_data.linked_prs %}
{%- for pr in structured_issue_data.linked_prs %}
- #{{ pr.number }} - {{ pr.url }} - {{ pr.title }} - {% if pr.merged %}(merged){% else %}(merged N/A){% endif %}  
{%- endfor %}
{%- else %}
_No linked PRs._  
{%- endif %}

**Grouped Links by Domain:**  
{%- for domain, links in structured_issue_data.grouped_links.items() %}
- **{{ domain }}**
    {%- for link in links %}
    - {{ link }}  
    {%- endfor %}
{%- endfor %}

**Referenced Events:**  
{%- set referenced_events = structured_issue_data.issue.timeline_items | selectattr('__class__.__name__', 'equalto', 'ReferencedEvent') | list %}
{%- if referenced_events %}
{%- for event in referenced_events %}
- **Type**: Commit  
  - **message**: {{ event.commit.message.strip() }}  
  - **oid**: {{ event.commit.oid }}  
  - **Date**: {{ event.created_at }}  
{%- endfor %}
{%- else %}
_No referenced events found._  
{%- endif %}

**Cross Referenced Events:**  
{%- set cross_events = structured_issue_data.issue.timeline_items | selectattr('__class__.__name__', 'equalto', 'CrossReferencedEvent') | list %}
{%- if cross_events %}
{%- for event in cross_events %}
- **Type**: {{ event.source.typename if event.source and event.source.typename else 'Unknown' }}  
  - **Title**: {{ event.source.title }}  
  - **URL**: {{ event.source.url if event.source and event.source.url else 'N/A' }}  
  - **Date**: {{ event.created_at }}  
{%- endfor %}
{%- else %}
_No cross-referenced events found._  
{%- endif %}
